                | &nbsp;on&nbsp;
                a(href="https://unsplash.com/") Unsplash
              li Colored exercise icons from 
                a(href="https://icons8.com/") Icons8
              li
                | Favicon by 
                a(href='http://www.freepik.com', title='Freepik') Freepik
                |  from 
                a(href='https://www.flaticon.com/', title='Flaticon') www.flaticon.com
